&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-537&quot;&gt;We are seeking an experienced &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-537&quot;&gt;Commercial Account Manager&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-537 citation-end-537&quot;&gt; to join our team and focus on expanding relationships with our existing commercial customers&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;span class=&quot;citation-536&quot;&gt;This role requires a strategic, growth-oriented professional with a proven track record in account management, particularly in scaling customer relationships and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-536&quot;&gt;increasing overall customer spend year over year&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-535 citation-end-535&quot;&gt;As the primary point of contact for a portfolio of commercial clients, you will be responsible for driving revenue growth, enhancing customer satisfaction, and developing long-term account plans that align with the customers&#39; evolving needs&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-534 citation-end-534&quot;&gt;Prior experience working with producers of wine, beer, spirits or other beverages or beverage wholesalers is highly desirable but not required&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-532 citation-end-532&quot;&gt;This is an individual contributor role&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-531&quot;&gt;Account Growth &amp;amp; Management:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-531 citation-end-531&quot;&gt; Manage a dedicated portfolio of existing Encompass customers&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;span class=&quot;citation-530 citation-end-530&quot;&gt;Meticulously prioritize renewal strategies and proactively identify opportunities to drive significant account growth through strategic upselling and cross-selling of relevant new products and services&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;span class=&quot;citation-529 citation-end-529&quot;&gt;Develop a comprehensive understanding of each customer&#39;s business needs and tailor solutions accordingly&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-528&quot;&gt;Retention &amp;amp; Risk Mitigation:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-528&quot;&gt; Assume full responsibility for achieving and consistently exceeding assigned &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-528&quot;&gt;customer retention targets&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-528 citation-end-528&quot;&gt; by implementing proactive engagement strategies&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;span class=&quot;citation-527 citation-end-527&quot;&gt;Analyze churn risks and develop effective mitigation plans to ensure long-term customer relationships.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-527 citation-end-527&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-526&quot;&gt;Relationship Management &amp;amp; Advisory:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;citation-526 citation-end-526&quot;&gt; Cultivate and maintain robust, enduring relationships with key customer stakeholders&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;span class=&quot;citation-525 citation-end-52

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;From maker to market, Encompass is revolutionizing how technology supports the modern beverage industry–from winemaking with our vintrace solution to beverage production and distribution with our Encompass solutions, we are unlocking new levels of growth and efficiency for our customers across the entire three-tier beverage supply chain.&amp;nbsp; Join our team of technology &amp;amp; beverage professionals as we drive innovation and modernization in one of the world’s oldest, and most passionate industries.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Encompass Technologies is the Maker-to-Market Digital Platform for the Modern Beverage Industry. We are modernizing the beverage supply chain to unlock new levels of growth and efficiency for our customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With our cloud-based, open software platform and extensive partner ecosystem, customers are empowered to confidently grow their businesses while streamlining processes and reducing expenses through data-driven insights and actions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The world’s leading producers, distributors, and retailers trust Encompass to help guide and transform their business’ accounting processes, production, inventory and warehouse management, sales and delivery, route planning, and so much more!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team is composed of brilliant innovators who move quickly, collaborate effectively, and deliver results that drive customer success. We create best practices, often defining problems and solving them before others are even aware of the status quo. We are out to change the Beverage Industry by finding better ways to solve problems. You can find out more about Encompass at EncompassTech.com.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Employees in this role are part of a broader customer delivery team responsible for new customer onboarding. Data Migration Consultants facilitate the one-time transfers of customer data into the Encompass Cloud Platform (ECP).&amp;nbsp; Data Migration Consultants follow standards and best practices to assure the quality, repeatability, performance, and scale of Encompass data migrations providing a high quality customer experience and limited rework.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Plan: &lt;/strong&gt;Work collaboratively with the Managing Consultant, customer data owners, and other Encompass project stakeholders to define data migration activities and schedule for new customer onboarding.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Migrate &amp;amp; Resolve&lt;/strong&gt;: Owns the migration of key customer data to drive the ECP system configuration and populate historical transactional data required for customers to go-live. This includes directly extracting data from legacy systems, working with customer stakeholders to populate import templates, importing the data into ECP, validating the data for accuracy and completeness, and working with the customer and project team to resolve issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execute&lt;/strong&gt;: Complete planned activities on time and within budget, consistent with the onboarding project plan, and to our standard of quality.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications and Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of ERP, route accounting, warehouse management, account/financial, and/or beverage production software solutions and delivery methods (preferred.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience extracting data from a variety of software platforms and delivery methods, including web-based, cloud-based systems, and middleware solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience migrating data between software systems using ETL/ELT systems and practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analytical and curious mindset and ability to follow structured delivery approach

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;From maker to market, Encompass is revolutionizing how technology supports the modern beverage industry–from winemaking with our vintrace solution to beverage production and distribution with our Encompass solutions, we are unlocking new levels of growth and efficiency for our customers across the entire three-tier beverage supply chain.&amp;nbsp; Join our team of technology &amp;amp; beverage professionals as we drive innovation and modernization in one of the world’s oldest, and most passionate industries.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Implementation Consultant supports the Professional Services team in delivering Encompass solutions aligned with customer goals. They collaborate with customer success, establish trust, and enhance product knowledge and onboarding methods. Key duties include configuring solutions, providing basic project management, coordinating activities, and resolving issues within Encompass. A successful consultant can configure solutions independently, specialize in specific solutions, implement add-ons, and effectively communicate with the services team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work as part of a project team to implement Encompass products aligned to our customers’ desired workflow (jobs to be done).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working from a high level design, lead customers through decisions which will inform system configuration.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understand and communicate the value of platform capabilities in the context of our customers&#39; needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a product and industry subject matter expert who can direct customers to analytics and reports to demonstrate business outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather customer information to help troubleshoot implementation related issues as they arise. This might require conducting additional research to identify root causes and coordinate a plan to resolve or mitigate the issue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use documentation and reference materials to enhance customer success, align with internal implementation configurations, and provide feedback for improving documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborates with internal teams (data migration, EDI, integration, etc.) to ensure projects meet deadlines, tests product fixes and new features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accomplish your assigned work within project parameters (deadlines, budgeted time and scope)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Record time accurately and achieve billable utilization targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree or equivalent relevant experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years experience leading implementations for ERP, warehouse management, account/financial, and/or beverage production software solutions and delivery methods.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize outstanding communication and presentation skills to contribute to projects while managing multiple priorities and activities to completion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use basic tools including MS Office, Visio, Google Suite, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Logical mindset and ability to follow structured delivery approaches, processes, and solution logic.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience in the beverage distribution or production industry preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position requires periodic overnight travel to customer sites, prospect locations, and to international offices. Additional travel includes attendance of company meetings and trade shows. This role may travel up to 50% of the time.&lt;/p&gt;
